<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="block-n">block <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /blɒk/    美 /blɑːk/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(木、石等的) 块；大块：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>block of</strong> ice / rock 
一块冰/岩石</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The floor was made of wooden blocks.
地板是由木块拼制而成的。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>街区：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She told us to go around the corner on the left and keep going straight for two blocks. 
她告诉我们向左转过这个拐角，一直向前走两个街区。</p><footer> 人教① – 2</footer></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>大楼；大厦：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an <strong>office / apartment block</strong> 
办公大楼/公寓楼</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.<strong>障碍 (物)；阻塞 (物)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a traffic block 
交通阻塞</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There was a block in the pipe and the water couldn’t flow. 
管内有阻塞物，水无法流动。</p></div>

<h4 id="5">5.<strong>一组；一批；一套：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Allow your children to study in blocks of time, such as for half an hour with a five-minute break in the middle. 
允许孩子用成组的时间学习，比如每学习半小时中间休息5分钟。</p><footer>2009 全国</footer></div></div>